				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Need Reply )<a name="17761"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 29 04 9:47 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>starting out you will want weapons that do not have a required level and pack a punch.  I recommend:
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=20525">Blackened Acrylia Blade</a> -  this runs in the 6-10k range and has a long life.  Its also something that resells well.
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6799">Di'Zok Wristsnapper</a> - this can be moved to our range slot for a boost to CHA and INT.
<br />

<br />
For chest slot, i would recommend
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=12184">Engraved Royal Velium Field Plate</a> -  this does not have a recommended level but if you don't have the pp the buy one of the very cheap LDoN crafted chest peices.  
<br />

<br />
In your 40s you can switch to:
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=23154">Architect's Bejeweled Chestplate</a>
<br />

<br />
HP items help enormously throughout your career.  6ac 65hp rings and Black Saphirre Electrum earrings are great investments and very cheap.  
<br />

<br />
Long term investments would be:
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16448">Troubadour's Mace</a>
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=17756">Battle Drummer's Main-Gauche</a>
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=18979">Cloak of Greater Pernicity</a>
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=12456">Earring of the Solstice</a>
<br />

<br />
hope this helps
<br />

<br />
pass on the swiftblade...its a nice twink weapon but you have more important investments to make.
<br />
</span></td>
